reviewText: two enjoyable films. roddy piper shows why he stayed a wrestler. plays a good role as sam hell. ok if you are a collector of sci-fi films.
Title: Def-Con 4 / Hell Comes to Frogtown

reviewText: I got this for Hell comes to frogtown. I saw it a long time ago and it is still bad.  But it is one of those movies that is so bad it is good and it comes with a bonus movie.
Title: Def-Con 4 / Hell Comes to Frogtown

reviewText: I haven't seen Def-Con 4 so I have no opinion on it, but Hell Comes to Frogtown is amazing. Very cheesy and funny and starring Roddy Piper. What else could you ask for in a movie with that ridiculous of a title?
summary: Got this for only one movie.
Title: Def-Con 4 / Hell Comes to Frogtown

reviewText: Def-Con 4 admittedly I did not finish but it is very dated and awesomely bad.Hell comes to Frogtown ... get your friends and some beers cause it is going to be a great night for this epic lost flick.
summary: What would you do if you returned to earth after the Nuclear War and found your high school sweet heart was the ruler?
Title: Def-Con 4 / Hell Comes to Frogtown

reviewText: I remember watching Hell comes to Frogtown as a kid long ago. Although this film is definitely dated it does have some amazing entertainment value if you like loads of cheese. A steal at only $4 and it came with another campy 80s movie too. Good times!
